parameters: It's already morning... Wake up quickly...
If you don't wake up soon... we'll be late for school...

I had a precious childhood friend. Despite being a girl, she
was stronger than anyone, smarter, and like a prince to me.

We lived next door to each other, and since we were young,
we always spent time together. Even after becoming students,
that didn't change, and I thought this happiness would
continue forever.

But one day, a transfer student arrived, and everything went
awry. My childhood friend caught the transfer student's eye,
was forcibly violated on her way home, and then threatened.

She was called out numerous times without my knowledge, and
subjected to terrible things... No, that's not right.
I actually knew. I had noticed the changes in her.

I could have helped her... but I was too scared to do
anything... too weak to do anything...

And this is the result. My childhood friend was corrupted by
the transfer student, and feeling responsible, I began to
shut myself away in a dim room.

The only source of light, the computer monitor, displays my
childhood friend's lewd figure today as well. I use it as
material for my pathetic masturbation, repeating the act
over and over.

My name is Sato Mamoru. This is a story of my regrets for
doing nothing.

And... it's the story after my childhood friend, who was
like a prince, became a sow.
～タイトル画像を画面中央に表示～
～タイトル画像を画面中央に表示～

"Ahhh... I failed to protect Makoto again... I couldn't
protect her, couldn't protect her, couldn't protect her...!"

"Hey, hey. Isn't that wrong, Mamoru? It's not that you
'couldn't protect' me, it's that you 'didn't protect' me,
right?"
"That's not true...! I've always cared about you deeply...!"

"Is that so? What have you done for me then? When I was
being threatened by Suzuki, did you even try to help me?"

"I-I tried to help! But there were guards around and... it
never went well..."

"If you weren't serious about helping, it's no wonder things
didn't work out, right? That's why a scumbag like me ended
up taking Makoto from you!"

"Shut up...! What do you know...! If you hadn't come to this
town in the first place... none of this would have
happened!"

"Nah, you're wrong. Whether I came or not, you would have
lost Makoto eventually."

"You've been too complacent about being Makoto's childhood
friend. If you don't take action yourself, even if I hadn't
shown up, your relationship would have fizzled out on its
own."

"I... I was planning to confess to Makoto properly...! Once
Golden Week came around... I was going to confess to
her...!"

"Hehehe. Mamoru, you're always just thinking. If thinking
alone could change reality, nobody would have any troubles."

"What matters is whether you can turn those thoughts into
action. When I decided to make Makoto fall, I acted on it
right away. Gyahahaha!"

"Hehehe... That's right. Because you did nothing, Mamoru, I
ended up like this, didn't I? Turned into a sow that can
only think about sex all day long."

"Stop it... please stop...! Don't blame me...! I've been
suffering every day since you were taken from me...!"

"Suffering~? Gyahahaha! Despite that, you always seem to
enjoy jerking off while watching the streams!"

"That was... to punish myself for doing nothing...! To
torment myself... in hopes of atoning even a little..."

"No, that's not it. You don't have such intentions. You got
excited because your precious childhood friend was taken
from you, didn't you? You've been enjoying watching my
downfall all along, haven't you?"
